Antibodies against phosphorylcholine in hospitalized versus non-hospitalized 
obese subjects.

Jujić A(1)(2)(3), Korduner J(4)(5), Holm H(4), Engström G(4), Bachus E(4), 
Bhattacharya P(6), Nilsson PM(4)(5), Frostegård J(#)(7), Magnusson 
