Radiotherapy Response Assessment of Multiple Myeloma: A Dual-Energy CT Approach 
With Virtual Non-Calcium Images.

Fervers P(1), Celik E(1), Bratke G(1), Maintz D(1), Baues C(2), Ruffing S(2), 
Pollman-Schweckhorst P(3), Kottlors J(1), Lennartz S(1), Große Hokamp N(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Radiology, University Hospital of Cologne, Cologne, Germany.
(2)Department of Radiotherapy and Cyberknife Center, University Hospital of 
Cologne, Cologne, Germany.
(3)Chair in Marketing Science and Analytics, University of Cologne, Cologne, 
